item.description:
Customization Review Use this page to review customization settings for dashboards.
To access this page;
 Select Admin &gt; Customization &gt; WebApp Customization in the Navigation pane. Click the Pages icon for a WebApp. Click the Review icon for a page. Click the Review icon for a user ID.           Field Description   USER ID Displays the user ID.   REVIEW Click to view the customization settings for the dashboard for the user.
